Class NewsSelectionView

  • java.lang.Object
    • NewsSelectionView

  • class NewsSelectionView
extends java.lang.Object
    This is default view for the user. It has two jlists and a menu bar full of fun goodies for the user to change the newsMakerlist .

    cglen
